Installation:
------------

Get lua 5.1.4 or newer, on Windows use 'luavs.bat' from the lua sources
to build it.

If you have an old Windows SWK which doesn't set LIBPATH and INCLUDES
use the supplied 'luavs.bat' script and set PLATFORM_SDK_DIR there
correctly.

links:

http://www.gamedev.net/reference/programming/features/CPPLuaExport/
